data.description: Welcome to your dream mountain home in the beautiful Eagles Landing subdivision! Private setting in town with a convenient location. Just minutes from shopping, dining, and beautiful Alpine Helen. Also, convenient drive to Gainesville, and surrounding communities. The exterior of the home has been recently painted and a new roof was placed in 2022. Inside features an open floor plan, large master with vaulted ceiling, double vanities, his and her closets, separate shower and spa air tub that has heated sides and lights. Granite countertops, tile floors, crown molding, and hardwood floors are just some of the upgrades in this home. Recently, the walk-out basement has been partially finished and can be used for entertaining or completed to make a separate living area. And let's not forget about the private back yard! Complete with a black chain link fence that gives extra security for your pets and family.
